  performance and efficiency improvements are small from generation to generation so don‚Äôt be afraid to buy a used machine.
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>On the end compare extremely expensive best 9gen. mobile CPU (8 cores) with a regular high-grade 8gen. desktop CPU (6 cores).</p>
